{"title": "matplotlib绘图(4) - 个人文章 ", "index": "python", "content": "本章我们主要学习的技能有：绘制饼图，填充区域。\n\n1 绘制饼图\nfrom pylab import *\nfigure(1,figsize=(6,6))\n\nax=axes([0.1,0.1,0.8,0.8])\nlabels=['Sping','Summer','Autumn','Winter']\nexplode=(0.02,0.1,0.1,0.2)\nx=[15,30,45,10]\n# explode爆炸 分裂 间隙  startangle 开始角度  默认从0开始，逆时针排列\npie(x,labels=labels,explode=explode,startangle=60,autopct='%1.1f%%')\n\nshow()\n\n2 填充区域\nfrom matplotlib.pyplot import  *\nimport numpy as np\n\nx=np.arange(0.0,2,0.01)\n\ny1=np.sin(2*np.pi*x)\ny2=1.2*np.sin(4*np.pi*x)\n\nfig=figure()\nax=gca()\n\nax.plot(x,y1,color='black')\nax.plot(x,y2,color='black')\n# 以X为定点选取Y值  where 条件   \nax.fill_between(x,y1,y2,where=y2>=y1,facecolors='darkblue',interpolate=True)\nax.fill_between(x,y1,y2,where=y2<=y1,facecolors='deeppink',interpolate=True)\n\nax.set_title('filled between')\nshow()\n\n\n                ", "mainLikeNum": ["0 "], "mainBookmarkNum": "1"}